There are two rounded edged handles on each side for easy transportation and compact design for fitting into any space. The Oceanstar 4-Tier bamboo shoe shelf will never look out of style and is the perfect solution for all your shoe and organization needs.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About Us: Oceanstar Design Group Inc. is a designer and one of the leading manufacturers of home and kitchen storage products, which focus on easy home décor storage and furnishing products. Our vision is to provide home improvement solutions at an affordable price. Visit us to find out more about Oceanstar Design Group Inc. Oceanstar 4-Tier Bamboo Shoe Rack Be free of clutter and keep your shoes neatly organized with the Oceanstar 4-Tier Bamboo Shoe Shelf. The shoe shelf features all around open slats for optimal air flow to minimize odor coming from the shoes. Made from bamboo, it is not only elegantly designed but also sturdy and made to last. The natural finish of the shoe rack gently balances any interior theme of your home or area. There are two rounded edged handles on each side for easy transportation and compact design for fitting into any space. The Oceanstar 4-Tier Bamboo Shoe Shelf will never look out of style and is the perfect solution for all your shoe and organization needs. Can fit up to 12-16 pairs of adult sized shoes Dimensions: 31.35 inch H x 10.7 inch D x 27 inch W Product weight: 11 lbs Easy assembly Care and Maintenance: When cleaning your furniture, use a non-toxic and non-abrasive cleaner. Apply to the surface with a soft, dry cloth, dampened in the solution. After cleaning, dry completely with a soft dry cloth.

Rounded Handles The shoe rack is designed with rounded handles to provide an aesthetically pleasing look. This design also offers greater comfort and easier portability when moving the shoe rack. In addition, these rounded edges prevent the risk of injury during transportation.

Slatted Tiers Each tier has a slatted design to enhance optimal air circulation and to prevent the buildup of odor. The multiple tiers can be used to hold any collection of your home accessories in addition to your shoe collection. Additionally, this design gives the shoe rack a contemporary look to your home environment.

Compact Size The shoe rack’s compact size makes it a perfect fit for any space in the home. It can fit in any corner or nook of your house. Moreover, it is lightweight, which enables easier portability throughout the house.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well made from natural materials. Efficient use of space to store shoes.
reviews.reviewText: Wood is good. The natural wood was pleasant to work with during assembly. All holes were located precisely. The wood is lightweight but seems strong and should be durable. Provides spaces big enough for 15 of my size 12 shoes. The design is functional, efficient and mazimizes use of the space. Very nice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 14, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my wife and she loves it. Before this, she had an inexpensive shoe rack that was made out of plastic and it was very flimsy. The only way to re-enforce it was using a bungee cord. I bought this for her and she is so happy with it. It fits perfectly under the window and holds lots of shoes.I can always tell about the quality of a product like this when I assemble it. This is very good quality. It is not fake wood, but solid bamboo. All the hardware is good quality. All the holes are drilled well and line up well, except for one hole. When I put the screw in that one hole I could hear the wood split. As soon as I hear it, I backed out the screw and re drilled that hole. I used some wood glue and a clamp and now it is perfect.I do not hold that small issue against my positive review because it was so easy to fix. I would highly recommend this shoe rack for anyone. Super high quality and worth every penny.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 21, 2021
reviews.reviewText: I love these shelves more than words can say. The are simple, but beautiful. I had a messy pile of shoes and random stuff on the floor of my closet and now it looks organized and there is so much floor space. I found cute canvas bins that fit perfectly on the shelves for my small items. The shelves are super easy to put together and very sturdy and solid. There are holes and joining pegs if you want to stack the shelves on top of each other. Just check the measurements so that you know what you are getting and if it will fit your needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Kindergarten Grocery Store
reviews.reviewText: I am a kindergarten teacher and have a classroom store for my students. My students are 5-6 years old and these are the perfect height for them being used as "store shelves" I bought 2 medium racks for them to use and it holds so many food items. If you do plan on using these for pretend play, note: the gaps in between are sometimes too big for the food items. You will need to put some weight to the food items to keep them from falling easily. Or you can add a tray on top of each shelf to prevent them from falling over. They have held up so nicely the last two years and will probably last for many more years!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 4, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice high-end spa look at a low-end price.
reviews.reviewText: We needed a compact piece more for looks to fill the space beneath our bathroom towel rack. This is perfect because it is so shallow, but wider and taller than other options we found. A great look and equally impressed with the amount of storage it offers.We have now seen several of this exact brand/piece already assembled in our local (national chain) discount home goods shop for a bit cheaper, but this was also easy to assemble.NOTE: Since these are technically sold as stackable shoe racks, it does come with 4 connector dowels plus 4 matching holes in the top and bottom, which are tough to spot in product photos so check out our review pics. Not so nice looking, but they can be quickly and easily disguised with wood putty, hole plugs from the hardware store, or just do like we did - cut the included dowels short enough then hammer in (finished end up of course) until they are flush.
